  "detailed_description": "Red Zirion is a retro shooting game with upgradeable attributes in the roguelike style.<br>Help the team of space mercenaries Red Zirion to find and destroy the threat from the Cyber Brain Mentor.<br>Game inspired by groups of heroes and animated series from the 80s.<br><br><strong>Red Zirion Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Random Levels<br></li><li> Unlockable characters<br></li><li> Play with a friend in coop mode<br></li><li> Letters are weapons, weapons from A to Z<br></li><li> Wall jump works like a dodge <br></li><li> Interesting and difficult bosses for you win</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1247400/extras/3e525959bd32eb92978dcdfaed717820.avif?t=1695469241\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
